<a name="jasarth_scale_wrist_guards"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Jasarth Scale Wrist Guards - AC 8</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/wrists.shtml">Wrists</a><BR>
Weight: 0.8 - BAR, DEF, ERU, HEF, HIE, HUM, IKS, ELF<BR>
Classes: <a href="/cleric/armour/wrists.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/wrists.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/wrists.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/shaman/armour/wrists.shtml">SHM</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/wrists.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(WIS +4) (CHA +4) </font>
<BR>
Found in Karnor's Castle.<BR>

